  are learning from each other all the time. They agree, argue, and discuss all kinds of topics. Sometimes witty, sometimes inane, 
  sometimes poignant - but always talking. They think and talk in real time - they are a bit slow though, so you'll see new sentences
  roughly every 5 seconds.
